    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        58.94,
        364.26,
        197.27,
        371.06
      ],
      "text": "veranderd in de samenstelling van uw bedrijf?",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        56.69,
        374.68,
        350.0,
        382.18
      ],
      "text": "Wat was de eerste volledige maand na de start, afstoting, fusie of wijziging van rechtsvorm?",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        58.94,
        385.3,
        364.93,
        392.1
      ],
      "text": "Eerste maand na overgang van onderneming juli 2019",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        56.69,
        395.72,
        263.94,
        403.22
      ],
      "text": "Wat was uw netto-omzet in de referentieperiode? (in hele euro’s)",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        58.94,
        406.34,
        364.19,
        413.14
      ],
      "text": "Netto-omzet (in hele euro’s) in referentieperiode € 725172",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        56.69,
        416.77,
        239.37,
        424.27
      ],
      "text": "Wat was uw netto-omzet in deze periode? (in hele euro’s)",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        58.94,
        427.38,
        364.19,
        434.18
      ],
      "text": "Netto-omzet (in hele euro’s) in periode waarover NOW is aangevraagd € 106243",
